{"tid":1949343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有請小鳯姐]一名31歲機動部隊男警初步確診新型肺炎","createTime":"2020-03-29T14:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T11:58:26.000Z","uid":326897,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5d2267db422eb02b0eacd7a108e4ade9e272b6c1","tid":1949343,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:30:52.000Z","msg":"一名31歲機動部隊男警初步確診新型肺炎 無外遊紀錄<br />\n2020-03-29 HKT 21:30<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517613-20200329.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517613-20200329.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=d9139c24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517613-20200329.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a62ddaf5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517613-20200329.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n警方表示，一名31歲男警員初步確診新型肺炎，他駐守西九龍總區，隸屬機動部隊，過去14日曾參與反罪惡巡邏，並無外遊記錄。他今日感到不適後到醫院求醫，初步測試證實對新型肺炎病毒呈陽性反應。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，等候衞生署進一步評估及建議前，與確診警員駐守同一小隊的所有警員，將停止與市民接觸的工作；所有在西九龍機動部隊行動基地工作的警員需配戴口罩，進出警署的人要量體溫，並已安排徹底清潔及消毒相關警署設施及警車，亦會靈活調派人手，確保緊急服務不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，將繼續與衞生署保持緊密聯繫，主動提供該名警員近日工作記錄和執勤表等，安排密切接觸者進入檢疫中心接受檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3萬又減一</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9178e7f86a553f194681daf451922274847a8967","tid":1949343,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:47:52.000Z","msg":"[更新版]到底大家撐唔撐港台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6b8cf833fff628bbdc8784a7c24491b85bf1991d","tid":1949343,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:58:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新型你老母！<br />\n支那武漢肺炎呀！</span></strong></span>"}]}